i think it reflects the epa reconsidering the importance of 
the public policy decision they were making he said 
i think that the information they received from the press and 
the scientific community was that there was a tremendous concern 
about the influence of the tobacco industry on this kind of 
scientific panel 
burns has worked on the surgeon generals reports on the dangers 
