already strained usisraeli relations are 
under new pressures following the bush administrations second 
vote against israel in the united nations despite a plea for 
understanding from jerusalem 
secretary of state james a baker iii and others in the 
administration who would like to see israel negotiate with 
palestinians arabs will try to repair the damage before it 
