united states germany switzerland and turkey as well as the 
international foundation for art research asking if the mosaics 
were stolen 
bauer called her efforts a few lastminute phone calls 
joining bauer in his opinion was judge wilbur pell judge 
richard cudahay issued a concurring opinion 
