precaustion but there were no reports of damage 
the richter scale is a measure of ground motion as recorded on 
seismographs every increase of one number means a tenfold increase 
in magnitude a quake measuring 6 on the scale is capable of severe 
damage and a tremor measuring 7 of widespread heavy damage 
