harassment of relief workers natsios said european donors have 
all but stopped helping 
the united states natsios said is willing to provide onethird 
of an emergency 300000ton food shipment needed to avert mass 
starvation an estimated 50000 tons of us donated food are 
already been stored in sudan he added 
but unless the sudanese government allows relief workers to 
distribute the food and turns to the international community for 
more help we will not be able to respond in time if the call for 
help goes out after people start dying 
