billion from 258 billion ual said from its headquarters in elk 
grove village ill 
the higher revenues were largely a function of uniteds 
continuing routeexpansion program which also was reflected in a 
nearly 12 percent increase in the number of miles flown on united 
airlines by paying passengers during the quarter 
